name: productsTemplates
viewQuery:
SELECT
  products.id,
  products.title,
  products.description,
  products.images,
  products.seller createdBy,
  ( products.`parentId` ISNULL ) isDefaultTemplate,
  products.created,
  products.updated
FROM 
  products 
WHERE 
  products.`isTemplate`

name: testProductsAvailable
viewQuery:
WITH prod AS (
  SELECT  
  ps.`productId`,
  COUNT(ps.`productId`) c
FROM `testProducts`p 
JOIN `testProductsStocks`ps ON ps.`productId` = p.id
  GROUP BY ps.`productId`
)
SELECT 
  (ROW_NUMBER() OVER()) as id,
  prod.`productId`,
  prod.c,
  ps.quantity,
  ps.`productFieldId`
FROM `testProducts`p 
JOIN prod ON prod.`productId` = p.id
JOIN `testProductsStocks`ps 
  ON ps.`productId` = p.id 
  AND CASE WHEN prod.c > 1 THEN ps.`productFieldId` != "" ELSE true END

name: userMessages
viewQuery:
SELECT
  messages.id,
  messages.id messageId,
  messages.content AS messageContent,
  messages.`isRead` AS messageIsRead,
  messages.created AS messageCreated,
  messages.updated AS messageUpdated,

  products.id AS productId,
  products.title AS productTitle,
  products.images AS productImages,
  
  senderUser.id AS senderId,
  senderUser.name AS senderUsername,
  senderUser.avatar AS senderAvatar,

  receiverUser.id AS receiverUserId,
  receiverUser.name AS receiverUserUsername,
  receiverUser.avatar AS receiverUserAvatar
FROM messages
LEFT JOIN products ON products.id = messages.product
LEFT JOIN users AS senderUser ON senderUser.id = messages.sender
LEFT JOIN users AS receiverUser ON receiverUser.id = messages.receiver

name: usersRoles
viewQuery:
SELECT 
  users.id, 
  users.email, 
  users.name, 
  users.avatar, 
  'default' as role 
FROM users;
